---
title: Citrusy Pork Tenderloin with Wild Rice and Kale
description: This meal combines sweet cranberries and orange tang with savory pecans, scallions, and kale. A quick toss with nutty wild rice bulks up this hearty and nutritious base for the juicy pork tenderloin.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-pork-tenderloin-w49-b52e0ebb.jpg
